      <title>保守党议员攻击布鲁克菲尔德和卡尼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/brookfield-carney-targeted-in-attack-by-conservative-lawmaker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布鲁克菲尔德资产管理公司 (Brookfield Asset Management) 和马克·卡尼 (Mark Carney) 成为加拿大保守党一名成员的目标，该成员希望加拿大游说监管机构对他们进行调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/brookfield-carney-targeted-in-attack-by-conservative-lawmaker</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 21:39:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国安理会谴责以色列将秘书长古特雷斯列入黑名单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/security-council-chides-israel-for-blacklisting-un-boss-guterres</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国安理会对以色列宣布该组织首席人物为不受欢迎的人的决定表示谴责，并表示任何使其工作非法化的举动都是适得其反的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/security-council-chides-israel-for-blacklisting-un-boss-guterres</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 21:26:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登视察海伦飓风灾区，称飓风灾后恢复将耗资数十亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/helene-hurricane-recovery-will-cost-billions-biden-says-after-tour</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登周四视察遭受飓风海伦袭击的地区时表示，恢复工作将耗资“数十亿美元”，并呼吁立法者确保提供额外资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/helene-hurricane-recovery-will-cost-billions-biden-says-after-tour</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 20:45:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
